Given $a\in\mathbb{R}$, let $f: (-\infty,a)\rightarrow \mathbb{R}$ and $g:[a,+\infty)\rightarrow \mathbb{R}$ be measurable functions. Show that the function $h:\mathbb{R}\rightarrow \mathbb{R}$ defined by
